 everywhere,
 in whatever coordinate chart we might like to work in.
 Yes,
 I rather like the Painleve coordinates,
 but this is besides the point;
 the topology of the base space 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 is fixed,
 it is not dynamical.
 Its nailed down.
\end_layout

